<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: firebrick; font-weight: bold;">诶哥别走啊，我这放人设。</span></p>
<div class="trans-quote">
<p>得得得得得得得。哦看在上帝的份上，如果你再欺骗我的话，我就会用隔壁<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/chris-evertworth" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6285604); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6285604&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610108844" alt="Chris Evertworth" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6285604)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/chris-evertworth" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6285604); return false;">Chris Evertworth</a></span>家几十年没洗的臭尖皮鞋狠狠的亲吻你的屁股。哦我发誓我会这么做的。</p>
