<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: firebrick; font-weight: bold;">哦你这只<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kcorena" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3396110); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3396110&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610108844" alt="Kcorena" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3396110)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kcorena" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3396110); return false;">Kcorena</a></span>家那只该死的鹅，瞧瞧你那糟糕的翻译腔，我发誓它简直像隔壁<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/brucewu0463" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5526785); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5526785&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610108844" alt="BruceWu0463" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5526785)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/brucewu0463" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5526785); return false;">BruceWu0463</a></span>家拥有6个乳房的猫娘一样令人厌恶，我发誓你是撒旦的手下。</span></p>
